metadata.title: Ice Transference of Bering Strait
metadata.description:
According to project of transport connection of USA and Russia across
        Bering Strait the three designs are considered: dam, underground tunnel,
        bridge. In all this cases a human influence on environment is great and must be
        accounted for even now. The paper presents the estimated changes of ice
        movements in Bering Strait. (DBO).
